title: The Sedgwick County Lady Cougar's
text: The Sedgwick County Lady Cougar's Posted: 10/15/2015 07:24:04   07:29:38 PM MDT Junior Jessica Kler and senior Bailey Fassler block against opponant during Friday s game against Merino.   Sedgwick County Lady Cougar's put up a fight during this weeks matches. They played Yuma, during their pink out game, and were defeated in three sets 25-8, 25-10, and 25-8. For the Lady Cougars it was also homecoming week, they faced the Merino Rams, and took them to four sets after winning the second set, but were swept. They have another busy week with three games. The girls are at home again this Tuesday for Parent's Night starting at 4 p.m. as they face the Leyton Warriors, then they head away for two games. Thursday night against Akron, and Caliche on Friday. Both games start at 4 p.m. Advertisement
